  - Prefer composition over deeply nested conditionals in JSX; extract small presentational components when render logic gets complex.

- **Error Handling & Async**
  - Always handle async errors (network, storage) explicitly; avoid empty `catch` blocks.
  - Fail gracefully in UI with safe fallbacks instead of crashing on unexpected data.
